<div class="page-header">
  <h1>Blackjack</h1>
</div>

<div class="row">
  <div class="span8">
    <div class="row actions">
      <div class="span 8">
        <%= link_to "Take Another Card", "#", class: 'btn btn-primary' %>
        <%= link_to "Start Over", "#", class: 'btn btn-primary' %>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="span8">
      <%= image_tag 'cards/2_of_hearts.png', width: 100 %>
      <%= image_tag 'cards/3_of_spades.png', width: 100 %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="span4">
    <h3>Challenges</h3>
    <strong>Consider an Ace to have a value of 1.</strong>
    <ol>
      <li>Deal two random cards from the deck.</li>
      <li>If the cards value 21, tell them they won!</li>
      <li>If the cards are over 21, tell them they lost.</li>
      <li>If they haven't won nor lost, allow them to take another card.</li>
      <li>Consider an Ace to have a value of 1 or 11, whichever is in the player's favor.</li>
    </ol>
  </div>
</div>
